    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkTitle
      value: Italian Brainrot Museum Specimen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkDescription
      value: "A fake museum display case containing a bizarre \u201CItalian brainrot\u201D
        creature: a cappuccino-headed crocodile wearing sneakers, with spaghetti
        for veins and tiny opera masks growing from its back. The creature is posed
        like an ancient fossil or rare animal specimen, labeled with unreadable pseudo-Latin
        text. The scene should look like a serious natural history museum preserving
        something completely stupid and internet-born. Photorealistic museum lighting,
        absurd character design, meme archaeology, artificial folklore, uncanny comedy,
        16:9."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
