    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkDescription
      value: A breathtaking aerial photograph of a modern city partially underwater
        after a fictional natural disaster. Boats move through streets, people gather
        on rooftops, and storm clouds hang overhead. It appears urgent and believable,
        yet landmarks are slightly wrong and repeating patterns emerge on closer
        look. The image should question how easily disaster imagery can persuade
        viewers. Drone photo realism, environmental drama, subtle uncanny details,
        16:9.
