    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkDescription
      value: A black-and-white archival style photograph showing a formal meeting
        between historical-looking figures inside a grand government hall. Vintage
        clothing, grainy texture, smoke in the air, official architecture, and serious
        expressions create the feeling of an important historical turning point.
        Yet symbols, uniforms, and faces contain subtle inconsistencies. The image
        should resemble a memory that never existed. Archival realism, old film texture,
        false history aesthetic, museum quality, 16:9.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
