      value: The Sacred Shrimp Algorithm
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkDescription
      value: A surreal AI-generated religious icon of a giant shrimp with too many
        tiny human hands, floating in the center of a glowing golden cathedral made
        of cheap plastic, surrounded by worshippers with blurred faces holding smartphones.
        The shrimp appears holy and ridiculous at the same time, with a halo made
        of loading symbols and social media like buttons. The image should feel like
        viral internet garbage pretending to be sacred art. Hyper-detailed, uncanny,
        absurd, overprocessed, glossy AI aesthetic, strange anatomy, excessive glow,
        meme culture, digital religious kitsch, synthetic spirituality, 16:9 cinematic
        composition.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
