    - target: {fileID: 9177908908250612626, guid: 1be7f228da16941f49e98881fbefa070, type: 3}
      propertyPath: artworkDescription
      value: 'A grotesque banquet table stretching endlessly into darkness, covered
        with impossible AI-generated food: pizza with eyes, burgers melting into
        faces, pasta shaped like human fingers, glowing blue sauce, fried chicken
        wings arranged like angel wings. Around the table sit faceless internet users,
        each staring at a phone instead of eating. The atmosphere should feel funny
        at first but disturbing after a closer look. Overloaded composition, chaotic
        details, viral content aesthetic, uncanny food, grotesque humor, artificial
        abundance, consumer culture, 16:9.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
